episodes.title: RTE Primetime - Scientology. An Ireland Cult.
episodes.description:
The Irish broadcast that yet again exposed Scientology for the family breaking, crazy, financial and dangerous cult madness that it truly is!
See: http://unitedpeople.ie/acultexposed for more.

episodes.title: CNN - Scientology: A History of Violence
episodes.description: In 2010, Anderson Cooper from CNN conducted a one-man crusade against those who evolved from the Planet Xenu. CNN conducted a week-long series on the history of violence inside the Church of Scientology. I have spliced these series segments together.
